Introduction

Yeham is a South Korean singer under A2Z Entertainment. She is the maknae and main vocalist of the girl group CSR.

In December 2023, Yeham was revealed to be a contestant on WeTV's survival show "Chuang Asia" alongside fellow CSR members Seoyeon, Geumhee and Duna.
